title: Spend 50 seconds with rookie Robyn Lawley, and get a little kiss! - Swim Daily -
text:
by Kelsey Hendrix Posted: Tue Oct. 13, 2015 Calling all Robyn Lawley fans! Prepare to fall even more in love with one of our favorite Aussie models of all time.
While stopping by the SI studio, Robyn sat down with Swim Daily to let readers know a little more about who she is. What's Robyn's favorite fast food? Which Australian phrases does she find that people Stateside always butcher?
Photo: James Macari/SI Watch the full "50 Seconds and a Kiss" video above to learn everything from her guilty pleasure (hint: it's ours, too!), to the designer she'd love to collaborate with on her swimwear line. We promise, these will be the best 50 seconds you'll spend all day long.
